  "title": "Kaliban",
  "description": "What happened to Shakespeare's immortal manbeast after the Tempest? Come explore the darkly comic hurdles faced by Kaliban as it struggles to fit in with an ever changing, shifting society, in a performance critic Leila Marston called \"beautifully lyrical and worthy of Shakespeare. A delight to the ears as well as the mind\"",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Andrew Hamilton<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Andrew Hamilton<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Andrew Hamilton<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Andrew Hamilton<br/>",
  "website": "",
